<p>AI detection tools have proliferated as AI-generated content has become mainstream. Many charge for full access, but several solid options are available for free. This guide compares the best free AI detection tools, explains what each one measures, and shows you what to expect from no-cost detection.</p>
<h2>What to Know Before Using Free AI Detectors</h2>
<p>Free tools have limitations. Understanding them helps you use these tools appropriately.</p>
<p><strong>Common free tool limitations:</strong></p>
<div class="table-wrap"><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Limitation</th>
<th>Typical Restriction</th>
</tr>
</thead>
